title: Nautica Men's Vintage Straight Denim Jeans
description: SUSTAINABLY CRAFTED: Our Real Denim collection is designed for the environmentally conscious; better jeans for a bluer world

A welcome departure from your standard everyday basic, these straight-leg jeans have all the design appointments you want-five-pocket styling, classic fit, button-and-zip closure-but in a cooler, more modern grey wash. They dress up or down, no sweat. From Nautica.
